snippet.title: The Sims 4 Outdoor Retreat: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Set up the perfect camp and explore Granite Falls in The Sims 4 Outdoor Retreat, available now!

Learn more about this Game Pack: http://bit.ly/1BWxQr2

Gather around the campfire and experience new gameplay, outfits and objects in the all-new outdoor destination.
